arStrings.szText: Enter the Courts of Night and slay the Vampire Lord Zir.
Lord Zir's thralls have fallen. Now nothing stands between me and the vampire lord himself. Time to end this.
Enter the City of the Ancients
I must meet Erys at the City of the Ancients. She will open the gate, but from there I must enter alone...and use Lord Zir's own power against him.
Meet Erys at the City of the Ancients
I felt my blood boil the moment I passed through the veil. Lord Zir's curse is trying to take hold. I have no choice but to press on and cut a path to his lair.
Approach the City of the Ancients
Erys has opened the gate. I must pass through the veil of blood and begin the hunt for Lord Zir.
Enter the City of the Ancients
